column5: Here's a link to some great trout tattoos and it's too bad there's no photo of the musky he did on my buddies arm........  http://www.sugarshacktattoo.com/Welcome.html  go to the tattoo link and fish are about half way down
Some nice ones the tribal ain't bad...
Some of his portraits are amazing. My brother in-laws family is in Kincardine, I may add some more ink next time now that I know this guy is there.
That guy has talent! He's got a year long waiting list to!
I've never gotten drunk enough to get a tattoo.
They won't do ya drunk..unless they know you.
Yesterday my Tatto said     SWAN Woke up this Morning it said     S-A-S-K-A-T-C-H-E-SWAN Will this get me in Trouble?
No trouble at all. You might not want to show your elementary school teacher how you spelled Saskatchewan though. Not to worry though, if she gives you a hard time, I'll back you.
